name: Keychain
description:
This is a customizable keychain with the free option of either a guitar pick, heart, oval, square or circle shaped blank. 

Additional accent charms can be added for an additional price. Charms can be anything from a simple heart, to a music note or something random like a pineapple! :) 

All products include a "Made with love" charm, unless otherwise specified.

name: Necklace
description:
This is a customizable necklace with the free option of either a guitar pick, heart, oval, square or circle shaped blank. You may also choose between a brown or black cord necklace. 

Additional accent charms can be added for an additional price. Charms can be anything from a simple heart, to a music note or something random like a pineapple! :) 

All products include a "Made with love" charm, unless otherwise specified.
